David Cameron might be the leader of the country but he has revealed that he is secretly a follower of TV cook Nigella Lawson.

The Prime Minister has admitted he is a member of #TeamNigella rooting for the Domestic Goddess in her very public battle with ex-husband Charles Saatchi.

Mr Cameron brushed aside her admission to snorting cocaine and smoking cannabis to hail her as a ‘very funny and warm person’ who creates good recipes.

